data.title: Born for Hell (1976) aka Naked Massacre
data.meta_description:
Heinz Funk Electric Combo - Scotch Whisky (1973) 
Music theme to Born for Hell/Naked Massacre (1976). the original film soundtrack only had 2 songs in the whole film, the title track "The Dingle Regatta" from a live Irish music festival album and this one by Heinz Funk album "Moog Synthesizer Music" on the Chappell library music label, the rest of the film was practically devoid of music, the video tape distributor decided to generically add some famous orchestra music upon releasing the home video and re-titled 'Naked Massacre".
